title: Non-contending Super Bowl teams
itunes:title: Non-contending Super Bowl teams
description:
A room with some heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal and Chris Wesseling -- are joined by NFL Now's Colleen Wolfe to discuss the latest NFL news including the Peyton Manning trade rumors (7:34). The guys also discuss if Geno Smith will make the leap in 2015 (22:15) and debate which teams have no shot at the Super Bowl this season (32:10). Plus, an all-new "Orr You Kidding Me?!".

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
